@BaseUrl = https://localhost:7001
@AuthToken = {{AuthToken}}

### User Calendar Endpoint

# Get user events
GET {{BaseUrl}}/api/calendar/user/events
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

###

### System Calendar Endpoint (Admin/Manager Only)

# Get all system events
GET {{BaseUrl}}/api/calendar/system/events
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}

